249
00:13:05,951 --> 00:13:08,554
Hee-young / Not for others
Seo-yeon / What happens if I don’t?

250
00:13:08,587 --> 00:13:11,257
Hee-young / Then you don’t, that’s all

251
00:13:19,331 --> 00:13:21,890
Seo-yeon / Ah

252
00:13:21,900 --> 00:13:24,326
Seo-yeon / I was going to just let it all go

253
00:13:24,336 --> 00:13:26,361
Seo-yeon / But today’s a special call day

254
00:13:26,371 --> 00:13:27,862
Seo-yeon / It’s not like the anonymous notes

255
00:13:27,872 --> 00:13:31,700
Seo-yeon / You can recognize me by my voice

256
00:13:31,710 --> 00:13:35,670
