276
00:15:33,165 --> 00:15:35,301
Seo-yeon / I think I just wanted to get rid of any regrets

277
00:15:35,334 --> 00:15:38,203
Seo-yeon / It felt kind of freeing

278
00:15:38,237 --> 00:15:40,863
Seo-yeon / Like really...

279
00:15:40,873 --> 00:15:43,765
Seo-yeon / Like I finally had no lingering feelings

280
00:15:43,775 --> 00:15:45,577
Seo-yeon / It felt clean

281
00:15:49,648 --> 00:15:52,641
Da-gyo / Huh?

282
00:15:52,651 --> 00:15:54,453
Da-gyo / Like this?

283
