295
00:16:25,584 --> 00:16:28,687
Mi-rang / Didn’t that make you feel a little drawn to her?

296
00:16:31,924 --> 00:16:34,526
Da-gyo / Honestly I was like, “How do I make this call?”

297
00:16:34,560 --> 00:16:35,561
Da-gyo / It was driving me crazy

298
00:16:35,594 --> 00:16:37,186
Da-gyo / The whole thing was just so embarrassing

299
00:16:37,196 --> 00:16:40,055
Da-gyo / I knew exactly who I wanted to call

300
00:16:40,065 --> 00:16:42,891
Da-gyo / But actually calling them...

301
00:16:42,901 --> 00:16:44,670
Da-gyo / I had no idea what to say

302
00:16:49,842 --> 00:16:52,578
Da-gyo / What should I say?

303
