Da-gyo / I kept thinking about what I wanted to say

304
00:16:54,513 --> 00:16:56,938
Da-gyo / It’s only 30 seconds, so what can I even say?

305
00:16:56,948 --> 00:16:59,040
Da-gyo / Anyway, when I heard her secret that day

306
00:16:59,050 --> 00:17:01,610
Da-gyo / That she had ADHD

307
00:17:01,620 --> 00:17:02,544
Da-gyo / I felt a little sorry

308
00:17:02,554 --> 00:17:04,723
Da-gyo / But even so, she tried so hard to be kind to me

309
00:17:04,757 --> 00:17:06,091
Da-gyo / She remembered what I said

310
00:17:06,125 --> 00:17:08,984
Da-gyo / And tried to take care of me in all these ways

311
00:17:08,994 --> 00:17:11,520
Da-gyo / So today I didn’t want to be vague

312
00:17:11,530 --> 00:17:13,399
Da-gyo / That’s why I made the call

313
00:17:15,467 --> 00:17:16,558
Mi-rang / Hello?

314
00:17:16,568 --> 00:17:20,094
Da-gyo / Unnie, it’s me, Da-gyo

315
00:17:20,104 --> 00:17:21,440
Mi-rang / Hello?

316
00:17:21,473 --> 00:17:25,544
Da-gyo / Mi-rang, it’s me, Da-gyo

317
00:17:26,145 --> 00:17:29,748
Da-gyo / I heard your secret today

318
