344
00:19:14,052 --> 00:19:17,589
Mi-rang / I’ll be back—ahh!

345
00:19:17,623 --> 00:19:22,227
Mi-rang / This is so hard to decide

346
00:19:25,030 --> 00:19:28,790
Mi-rang / I kept thinking, "How can I express my feelings"

347
00:19:28,800 --> 00:19:32,337
