00:19:38,911 --> 00:19:41,713
Mi-rang / Ah... 30 seconds

351
00:19:47,953 --> 00:19:51,323
Mi-rang / I thought I wouldn’t be nervous, but I was shaking so much

352
00:19:56,795 --> 00:19:59,231
