353
00:19:59,431 --> 00:20:01,533
Da-gyo / So I was like, what’s going on?

354
00:20:02,534 --> 00:20:06,305
Mi-rang / Ugh... I’m so nervous

355
00:20:23,355 --> 00:20:25,313
Da-gyo / Hello?

356
00:20:25,323 --> 00:20:27,426
Mi-rang / It’s me, Mi-rang

357
00:20:27,459 --> 00:20:28,527
Da-gyo / Yeah

358
00:20:32,130 --> 00:20:34,399
Da-gyo / Huh?

359
00:20:34,433 --> 00:20:38,293
Mi-rang / I like you more each day

360
00:20:38,303 --> 00:20:42,931
Mi-rang / I miss you, and I get jealous too

361
00:20:42,941 --> 00:20:44,376
Mi-rang / And...

362
00:20:50,315 --> 00:20:54,776
Mi-rang / Anyway, I miss you even now

363
00:20:54,786 --> 00:20:58,857
Mi-rang / I’m coming to see you right now

364
00:21:06,064 --> 00:21:09,067
Mi-rang / I think I fully expressed how I feel

365
00:21:13,872 --> 00:21:18,000
