401
00:23:47,159 --> 00:23:49,017
Han-kyul / I felt like I had to reply to the one who called me

402
00:23:49,027 --> 00:23:51,420
Han-kyul / And I had something I wanted to say too

403
00:23:51,430 --> 00:23:54,833
