406
00:24:04,876 --> 00:24:07,312
Han-kyul / Hello?

407
00:24:07,345 --> 00:24:09,080
Jin-ah / Ugh this is so unfair

408
00:24:09,114 --> 00:24:11,950
Jin-ah / Just because I called first

409
00:24:14,786 --> 00:24:15,944
Jin-ah / Ugh...

410
00:24:15,954 --> 00:24:18,980
Jin-ah / Now I made this boring

411
00:24:18,990 --> 00:24:22,049
