Han-kyul / The call had ended but

426
00:25:13,878 --> 00:25:15,480
Han-kyul / I just kept talking

427
00:25:15,514 --> 00:25:18,707
Han-kyul / I just wanted to say it

428
00:25:18,717 --> 00:25:22,554
