00:27:15,367 --> 00:27:16,801
Han-kyul / It could be a turning point

476
00:27:16,968 --> 00:27:20,572
Han-kyul / So go!
Ri-won / Okay

477
00:27:22,207 --> 00:27:26,034
Han-kyul / With Ri-won, I kept thinking, 'Why is she caring about me and not herself?'

478
00:27:26,044 --> 00:27:30,939
Han-kyul / So I felt thankful and sorry at the same time

479
00:27:30,949 --> 00:27:36,021
Han-kyul / But to be honest, I didn’t really feel any romantic feelings

480
00:27:42,360 --> 00:27:45,196
Ri-won / I really hate this

481
00:27:50,935 --> 00:27:55,096
Ri-won / Normally I don’t take long to write a note

482
00:27:55,106 --> 00:27:57,966
Ri-won / But I really hesitated when it came to calling

483
00:27:57,976 --> 00:28:01,002
Ri-won / Because you get an immediate response on the phone

484
00:28:01,012 --> 00:28:03,505
Ri-won / You can instantly see their reaction too

485
00:28:03,515 --> 00:28:05,306
Ri-won / Right before I left, Han-kyul said

486
00:28:05,316 --> 00:28:08,677
Ri-won / “Don’t call the person you’ve been writing notes to!”

487
00:28:08,687 --> 00:28:10,455
Ri-won / That’s what she told me

488
00:28:10,588 --> 00:28:14,616
Ri-won / So I thought, ‘Should I call someone else for her sake?’

489
00:28:14,626 --> 00:28:19,531
Ri-won / But… that would be a lie

490
00:28:36,281 --> 00:28:37,549
Ri-won / Hello?

491
00:28:40,452 --> 00:28:41,953
Ri-won / Uh...

492
00:28:43,788 --> 00:28:46,181
Ri-won / Hmm

493
00:28:46,191 --> 00:28:51,886
Ri-won / It’s just… ever since the date today

494
00:28:51,896 --> 00:28:56,458
Ri-won / They said to call the person you like

495
00:28:56,468 --> 00:29:00,939
Han-kyul / You really don't listen, do you

496
00:29:01,573 --> 00:29:04,432
Ri-won / I called the person I like

497
00:29:04,442 --> 00:29:06,945
Ri-won / Yeah...

498
00:29:12,250 --> 00:29:16,821
Han-kyul / Don’t keep making me feel bad, seriously...!

499
00:29:28,800 --> 00:29:30,925
Ri-won / From Han-kyul’s perspective

500
00:29:30,935 --> 00:29:34,028
Ri-won / I don’t think she understands why I like her

501
00:29:34,038 --> 00:29:35,797
Ri-won / Like, “Why me?”

502
00:29:35,807 --> 00:29:38,209
Ri-won / She seems to keep wondering that

503
00:29:38,443 --> 00:29:40,201
Ri-won / I'm not a fool, you know

504
00:29:40,211 --> 00:29:41,503
Ri-won / I know too

505
00:29:41,513 --> 00:29:43,471
Ri-won / Of course I know

506
00:29:43,481 --> 00:29:46,708
Ri-won / But I just...

507
00:29:46,718 --> 00:29:48,476
Ri-won / Ended up liking Han-kyul

508
00:29:48,486 --> 00:29:52,080
Ri-won / When I first sent her a note

509
00:29:52,090 --> 00:29:54,315
Ri-won / It wasn’t really like that

510
00:29:54,325 --> 00:29:58,429
Ri-won / But without realizing it, little by little...

511
00:29:58,530 --> 00:30:00,755
Ri-won / That’s how it happened

512
00:30:00,765 --> 00:30:02,934
Ri-won / What am I supposed to do

513
00:30:06,971 --> 00:30:08,663
Ri-won / Why are you scolding me?

514
00:30:08,673 --> 00:30:10,064
Han-kyul / Ri-won!

515
00:30:10,074 --> 00:30:12,433
Han-kyul / I told you, didn’t I

516
00:30:12,443 --> 00:30:14,102
Ri-won / Why are you getting mad?

517
00:30:14,112 --> 00:30:18,106
Han-kyul / I told you to go for someone else

518
00:30:18,116 --> 00:30:21,643
Ri-won / But you also told me to call the person I like

519
00:30:21,653 --> 00:30:23,978
Han-kyul / Still

520
00:30:23,988 --> 00:30:27,015
Han-kyul / That feeling of...

521
00:30:27,025 --> 00:30:29,894
Han-kyul / Waiting for a reply that might never come—don’t you regret that time?

522
00:30:30,061 --> 00:30:32,353
Ri-won / I don’t regret it at all

523
00:30:32,363 --> 00:30:34,699
Han-kyul / But then you don’t gain anything

524
00:30:35,466 --> 00:30:39,204
Ri-won / Why do you think that?

525
00:30:39,237 --> 00:30:42,040
Han-kyul / Do you think there’s still something to gain from this?

526
00:30:42,874 --> 00:30:46,044
Ri-won / Yes!

527
00:30:48,012 --> 00:30:50,982
Han-kyul / Geez...

528
00:30:52,050 --> 00:30:55,019
Han-kyul / Seriously...

529
00:30:56,454 --> 00:30:58,690
Han-kyul / Why do you keep making me feel so sorry

530
00:30:59,724 --> 00:31:03,885
Ri-won / You said you were sorry about that before

531
00:31:03,895 --> 00:31:06,264
Ri-won / But today...

532
00:31:11,269 --> 00:31:14,839
Han-kyul / Please stop making me feel bad

533
00:31:16,207 --> 00:31:19,400
Ri-won / What do you want me to do?

534
00:31:19,410 --> 00:31:23,838
Han-kyul / Can’t you open yourself up to other possibilities with different people?

535
00:31:23,848 --> 00:31:25,783
Han-kyul / I think you still have enough time to do that

536
00:31:30,688 --> 00:31:33,024
Ri-won / I’m just not the kind of person who can do that

537
00:31:44,035 --> 00:31:46,160
Ri-won / I felt like I was about to cry

538
00:31:46,170 --> 00:31:49,430
Ri-won / So I didn’t think I could say anything more

539
00:31:49,440 --> 00:31:51,009
Ri-won / I was holding back tears so much

540
00:31:53,378 --> 00:31:55,203
Ri-won / I’m going to go get some water

541
00:31:55,213 --> 00:31:57,715
Han-kyul / I’m gonna have a beer

542
00:32:14,465 --> 00:32:18,059
Ri-won / I could never cry in front of Han-kyul

543
00:32:18,069 --> 00:32:20,595
Ri-won / So I just stayed in the bathroom

544
00:32:20,605 --> 00:32:25,410
Ri-won / Ever since the phone call

545
00:32:25,543 --> 00:32:28,102
Ri-won / I kept feeling like I was going to cry, even though I didn’t want to

546
00:32:28,112 --> 00:32:30,214
Ri-won / So I went back in

547
00:32:30,715 --> 00:32:35,510
Ri-won / But if I cry, how would Han-kyul feel?

548
00:32:35,520 --> 00:32:40,748
Ri-won / I’ll never cry in front of Han-kyul again

549
00:32:40,758 --> 00:32:44,262
Ri-won / Never in front of Han-kyul

550
00:32:57,809 --> 00:33:01,836
Jin-ah / I didn’t say this because I thought I had a delusion of grandeur

551
00:33:01,846 --> 00:33:04,449
Jin-ah / And Ri-won unnie told me she liked Han-kyul

552
00:33:04,482 --> 00:33:05,550
Jin-ah / She said it clearly

553
00:33:05,583 --> 00:33:07,875
Jin-ah / But then with Han-kyul and me

554
00:33:07,885 --> 00:33:11,389
Jin-ah / Ever since we talked about my job and books

555
00:33:11,422 --> 00:33:15,016
Jin-ah / We’ve been making eye contact so much

556
00:33:15,026 --> 00:33:20,621
Jin-ah / Before that, we never made eye contact
Da-gyo / With Han-kyul?

557
00:33:20,631 --> 00:33:24,625
Jin-ah / I was even avoiding talking to her
Da-gyo / You talked a lot today though

558
00:33:24,635 --> 00:33:26,404
Jin-ah / That’s because

559
00:33:26,738 --> 00:33:29,797
Jin-ah / Han-kyul suddenly stopped calling me unnie

560
00:33:29,807 --> 00:33:31,466
Jin-ah / and started calling me “you”

561
00:33:31,476 --> 00:33:33,968
Da-gyo / Seriously? Since when?

562
00:33:33,978 --> 00:33:35,747
Jin-ah / I was giving an example with younger people

563
00:33:35,780 --> 00:33:36,904
Da-gyo / Right after that?

564
00:33:36,914 --> 00:33:37,805
Da-gyo / When did you talk about that?

565
00:33:37,815 --> 00:33:42,086
Da-gyo / After your secret talk? While sitting?
Jin-ah / Yeah, after the secret talk, we had a chat

566
00:33:42,487 --> 00:33:46,957
Jin-ah / I was worried it’d leave a trauma in her subconsciously
Da-gyo / After that conversation

567
00:33:46,958 --> 00:33:49,627
Jin-ah / The experience I kept feeling here

568
00:33:49,660 --> 00:33:51,285
Jin-ah / The shrinking experience

569
00:33:51,295 --> 00:33:54,032
Jin-ah / Being all timid in front of members

570
00:33:55,266 --> 00:33:57,125
Jin-ah / Should we go to the living room?

571
00:33:57,135 --> 00:33:58,036
Da-gyo / Shall we head out?

572
00:34:05,410 --> 00:34:08,002
Jin-ah / Like calling names, for example

573
00:34:08,012 --> 00:34:10,314
Jin-ah / Until now it’s always been "Unnie, I’m your fan"

574
00:34:10,348 --> 00:34:12,283
Jin-ah / "Unnie, let’s talk about books" and then suddenly

575
00:34:12,316 --> 00:34:13,841
Jin-ah / From that moment she started saying “you too”

576
00:34:13,851 --> 00:34:15,643
Jin-ah / Like that, nonstop

577
00:34:15,653 --> 00:34:17,111
Da-gyo / That’s honestly really cute though

578
00:34:17,121 --> 00:34:20,825
Da-gyo / You can tell when someone’s being obvious like that
Jin-ah / That too, yeah

579
00:34:20,858 --> 00:34:24,662
Da-gyo / So did you call Han-kyul today?

580
00:34:25,163 --> 00:34:28,132
Jin-ah / That Han-kyul is such a dummy

581
00:34:28,166 --> 00:34:31,636
Jin-ah / She just dropped the call knowing I know her past

582
00:34:34,839 --> 00:34:37,632
Da-gyo / Wait what? She called you?

583
00:34:37,642 --> 00:34:38,833
Da-gyo / You two called each other?

584
00:34:38,843 --> 00:34:39,410
Jin-ah / Yep hehe

585
00:34:41,045 --> 00:34:42,403
Jin-ah / And the funniest thing is

586
00:34:42,413 --> 00:34:44,282
Jin-ah / Han-kyul said she asked me out yesterday

587
00:34:44,315 --> 00:34:45,550
Da-gyo / Seriously?

588
00:34:46,350 --> 00:34:47,574
Jin-ah / That’s why it got messy

589
00:34:47,584 --> 00:34:49,787
Jin-ah / That mess with Hee-young unnie yesterday

590
00:34:49,821 --> 00:34:51,589
Jin-ah / They couldn’t go on the date

591
00:34:52,657 --> 00:34:54,192
Da-gyo / Oh my gosh, really?

592
00:34:56,327 --> 00:34:59,831
Da-gyo / I’m seriously shocked~

593
00:35:00,098 --> 00:35:03,357
Jin-ah / During the kart ride, Han-kyul told me

594
00:35:03,367 --> 00:35:05,493
Jin-ah / She asked me out

595
00:35:05,503 --> 00:35:09,340
Jin-ah / What kind of girl says "I asked you out"? That’s exciting

596
00:35:09,373 --> 00:35:10,174
Jin-ah / How could I not feel butterflies?

597
00:35:15,012 --> 00:35:17,982
Jin-ah / So it’s funny to me

598
00:35:18,015 --> 00:35:19,717
Jin-ah / We weren’t even having a serious emotional call

599
00:35:19,750 --> 00:35:22,075
Jin-ah / Saying “I like you” or anything

600
00:35:22,085 --> 00:35:23,845
Da-gyo / Yeah, I was really surprised too honestly

601
00:35:23,855 --> 00:35:26,914
Da-gyo / I really didn’t see that coming

602
00:35:26,924 --> 00:35:29,549
Jin-ah / What I thought was—

603
00:35:29,559 --> 00:35:32,085
Jin-ah / If she were older than me, I think I would’ve liked her

604
00:35:32,095 --> 00:35:33,431
Jin-ah / You know that kind of vibe?

605
00:35:34,132 --> 00:35:36,701
Da-gyo / I seriously love this kind of relationship

606
00:35:36,700 --> 00:35:38,459
Da-gyo / I never saw that coming
Jin-ah / That’s why I find it fun now

607
00:35:38,469 --> 00:35:40,928
Jin-ah / Now that I’ve fallen into this relationship too

608
00:35:40,938 --> 00:35:43,040
Jin-ah / At first I was only clinging to Hee-young unnie

609
00:35:43,074 --> 00:35:44,242
Jin-ah / But now

610
00:35:44,275 --> 00:35:46,934
Jin-ah / Honestly speaking, I knew we weren’t a match

611
00:35:46,944 --> 00:35:48,368
Jin-ah / But I kept trying to make it work

612
00:35:48,378 --> 00:35:50,013
Jin-ah / And I think that’s what caused this mess

613
00:36:00,992 --> 00:36:02,460
Min-woo / But now

614
00:36:02,493 --> 00:36:05,129
Min-woo / I got three notes yesterday

615
00:36:07,365 --> 00:36:11,058
Min-woo / Not all of them were nice, though

616
00:36:11,068 --> 00:36:15,006
Min-woo / One of them looked like your handwriting

617
00:36:15,039 --> 00:36:19,400
Mi-rang / Huh? Me?, I didn’t write anything to you

618
00:36:19,410 --> 00:36:23,104
Min-woo / No, not a love note
Mi-rang / A sabotage one?

619
00:36:23,114 --> 00:36:25,206
Mi-rang / Not at all

620
00:36:25,216 --> 00:36:27,942
Mi-rang / What’s wrong with my handwriting, seriously

621
00:36:27,952 --> 00:36:30,788
Mi-rang / Why does everyone assume the messy one is mine?

622
00:36:34,458 --> 00:36:36,627
Mi-rang / I wrote a sabotage note to Hee-young

623
00:36:39,630 --> 00:36:41,522
Min-woo / Oh then maybe the two of you...

624
00:36:41,532 --> 00:36:45,403
Min-woo / Maybe there really *is* something going on

625
00:36:46,103 --> 00:36:51,731
Mi-rang / But today, after their date

626
00:36:51,741 --> 00:36:54,178
Mi-rang / They seem a lot closer now

627
00:36:55,112 --> 00:37:00,051
Mi-rang / I feel like Hee-young might’ve called Da-gyo

628
00:37:02,954 --> 00:37:05,146
Min-woo / But now

629
00:37:05,156 --> 00:37:08,526
Min-woo / From what I feel

630
00:37:09,160 --> 00:37:13,531
Min-woo / Since I share a room with Seo-yeon

631
00:37:13,564 --> 00:37:16,334
Min-woo / We say it’s friendship but

632
00:37:17,101 --> 00:37:18,869
Min-woo / I thought it was Seo-yeon

633
00:37:19,237 --> 00:37:23,674
Min-woo / I think it was after she revealed her secret

634
00:37:24,141 --> 00:37:26,500
Min-woo / Hee-young is more emotional than I thought

635
00:37:26,510 --> 00:37:29,670
Min-woo / She has more sensitivity

636
00:37:29,680 --> 00:37:32,516
Min-woo / That’s the impression I got

637
00:37:47,231 --> 00:37:50,434
Mi-rang / Unnie!

638
00:37:51,369 --> 00:37:52,670
Mi-rang / What’s wrong?

639
00:38:13,124 --> 00:38:16,093
Ri-won / Don’t talk to me

640
00:38:36,414 --> 00:38:40,374
Ri-won / If you’re feeling uncomfortable right now

641
00:38:40,384 --> 00:38:45,890
Ri-won / I really don’t have any intention of making you feel that way

642
00:38:46,791 --> 00:38:50,318
Ri-won / I keep picking you, right?

643
00:38:50,328 --> 00:38:54,131
Ri-won / Is that maybe too much for you? Does it feel uncomfortable?

644
00:38:57,234 --> 00:38:59,493
Han-kyul / I’m going to be really honest

645
00:38:59,503 --> 00:39:02,897
Han-kyul / Is there really no one else here you’re interested in besides me?

646
00:39:02,907 --> 00:39:07,268
Ri-won / If I go back to the beginning

647
00:39:07,278 --> 00:39:12,540
Ri-won / When I first got here, there wasn’t anyone I liked

648
00:39:12,550 --> 00:39:15,109
Ri-won / I didn’t have anyone in mind

649
00:39:15,119 --> 00:39:18,579
Ri-won / But they told us to pick someone based on first impression

650
00:39:18,589 --> 00:39:22,216
Ri-won / Seo-yeon’s smile looked really pretty

651
00:39:22,226 --> 00:39:24,952
Ri-won / So I picked Seo-yeon and said “You have a nice smile”

652
00:39:24,962 --> 00:39:28,566
Ri-won / Then I started talking to you

653
00:39:28,666 --> 00:39:33,861
Ri-won / And somehow I started developing feelings for you

654
00:39:33,871 --> 00:39:37,331
Ri-won / Then when I had to write a note

655
00:39:37,341 --> 00:39:40,067
Ri-won / I couldn’t think of anyone else but you

656
00:39:40,077 --> 00:39:45,139
Ri-won / So I wrote you the note, and my feelings grew stronger

657
00:39:45,149 --> 00:39:49,920
Ri-won / I kept writing it because I liked you

658
00:39:52,490 --> 00:39:55,549
Ri-won / If I write one again, it’ll be for you

659
00:39:55,559 --> 00:39:57,785
Ri-won / But if that’s too much for you

660
00:39:57,795 --> 00:40:00,755
Ri-won / And if it makes you feel sorry or uncomfortable

661
00:40:00,765 --> 00:40:04,058
Ri-won / Then I’ll write to someone else if you want me to

662
00:40:04,068 --> 00:40:09,206
“But it won’t be because I like that person”

663
00:40:17,214 --> 00:40:21,242
Ri-won / I kind of felt like you kept feeling sorry toward me

664
00:40:21,252 --> 00:40:25,556
Ri-won / That’s how it felt to me

665
00:40:25,923 --> 00:40:31,385
Ri-won / But I’ve never once expected you to write a note for me

666
00:40:31,395 --> 00:40:32,853
Ri-won / Not even once

667
00:40:32,863 --> 00:40:36,924
Han-kyul / But that makes me feel even more sorry

668
00:40:36,934 --> 00:40:42,596
Han-kyul / Why don’t you even consider writing to someone else?

669
00:40:42,606 --> 00:40:45,499
Han-kyul / Is it just because you’re worried I’ll get zero votes?

670
00:40:45,509 --> 00:40:48,202
Ri-won / It wasn’t like that the whole time—it was just at first

671
00:40:48,212 --> 00:40:50,738
Ri-won / Just at the beginning

672
00:40:50,748 --> 00:40:56,610
Han-kyul / But if you don’t write one for me, you think I’ll end up with zero votes

673
00:40:56,620 --> 00:41:01,792
Han-kyul / But I wouldn’t be hurt by that

674
00:41:02,326 --> 00:41:04,819
Han-kyul / And even if you keep writing to me

675
00:41:04,829 --> 00:41:06,787
Han-kyul / I won’t get annoyed

676
00:41:06,797 --> 00:41:11,158
Han-kyul / But I think I’ll just keep feeling sorry about it

677
00:41:11,168 --> 00:41:22,146
Han-kyul / So if you don’t want to pretend, just be honest with yourself

678
00:41:22,313 --> 00:41:24,548
Ri-won / Yeah, honestly, I don’t want to pretend

679
00:41:24,682 --> 00:41:26,974
Ri-won / That’s not who I am

680
00:41:26,984 --> 00:41:30,344
Ri-won / And I want you

681
00:41:30,354 --> 00:41:34,758
Ri-won / To keep writing to the person you really want to

682
00:41:38,095 --> 00:41:45,726
Ri-won / When I got here and looked around

683
00:41:45,736 --> 00:41:48,295
Ri-won / You just looked like a good person to me

684
00:41:48,305 --> 00:41:50,798
Ri-won / So I just kept writing to you

685
00:41:50,808 --> 00:41:53,901
Ri-won / But because you keep feeling sorry, I start overthinking it

686
00:41:53,911 --> 00:41:55,603
Ri-won / You really don’t need to feel sorry

687
00:41:55,613 --> 00:41:57,848
Han-kyul / But I do feel sorry

688
00:41:57,948 --> 00:41:59,683
Han-kyul / And you feel bothered that I feel that way

689
00:42:02,319 --> 00:42:03,577
Ri-won / But there’s no reason to

690
00:42:03,587 --> 00:42:07,014
Ri-won / It’s not like this is my last chance in life or anything

691
00:42:07,024 --> 00:42:08,082
Han-kyul / Of course it’s not

692
00:42:08,092 --> 00:42:10,628
Ri-won / So why do you keep apologizing?

693
00:42:16,834 --> 00:42:18,859
Han-kyul / Maybe...

694
00:42:18,869 --> 00:42:22,306
Han-kyul / Feeling sorry itself might actually be ignoring your feelings

695
00:42:30,481 --> 00:42:37,988
Han-kyul / It’s your heart—we can’t tell you what to do with it

696
00:42:38,556 --> 00:42:43,217
Han-kyul / Honestly, at first, I just felt sorry

697
00:42:43,227 --> 00:42:46,830
Han-kyul / I kept thinking, “Why is she caring about me instead of herself?”

698
00:42:46,931 --> 00:42:50,834
Han-kyul / I felt thankful and sorry

699
00:42:51,435 --> 00:42:54,662
Han-kyul / But now that I think about it, maybe being sorry itself

