Ri-won / What are you thanking me for?

926
00:54:17,320 --> 00:54:18,911
Ri-won / I’ll do it for you every day until we leave

927
00:54:18,921 --> 00:54:22,749
Han-kyul / Whoa… I feel like I should be paying you

928
