Ri-won / You don’t need to pay

929
00:54:26,529 --> 00:54:28,231
Han-kyul / I’ll get going now
Ri-won / Go ahead~

930
00:54:28,264 --> 00:54:29,956
Han-kyul / Thank you
Ri-won / Have fun~

931
00:54:29,966 --> 00:54:31,290
Hee-young / Can I come up?

932
00:54:31,300 --> 00:54:32,468
Ri-won / Yes

933
00:54:34,203 --> 00:54:37,964
Hee-young / Wow, you look so pretty

934
00:54:37,974 --> 00:54:41,411
Hee-young / Off on a date, huh?

935
00:54:45,815 --> 00:54:51,043
Han-kyul / Jin-ah gave off this deep, emotional vibe

936
00:54:51,053 --> 00:54:55,314
Han-kyul / I wanted to take away that lonely feeling she had

937
00:54:55,324 --> 00:54:59,152
Han-kyul / Honestly, the keyword “responsibility” was really big for me

938
00:54:59,162 --> 00:55:03,699
Han-kyul / I wanted to change her emotions, comfort her

939
00:55:10,373 --> 00:55:12,532
Da-gyo / Whoa, you look gorgeous today

940
00:55:12,542 --> 00:55:14,277
Han-kyul / Shall we go now?

941
00:55:20,716 --> 00:55:22,442
Mi-rang / Shall we go?

942
00:55:22,452 --> 00:55:24,811
Mi-rang / Want to go?

943
00:55:24,821 --> 00:55:27,713
Mi-rang / Da-gyo, would you like to go with me?

944
00:55:27,723 --> 00:55:29,248
Jin-ah / Go out into the world!

945
00:55:29,258 --> 00:55:33,286
Jin-ah / I was like, “What do I do with this younger woman full of mature charm?”

946
00:55:33,296 --> 00:55:35,154
Jin-ah / She really dressed up beautifully

947
00:55:35,164 --> 00:55:39,025
Jin-ah / When someone you’re interested in usually looks casual

948
00:55:39,035 --> 00:55:42,595
Jin-ah / And then dresses up just for a date with you

949
00:55:42,605 --> 00:55:45,508
Jin-ah / That feeling is seriously thrilling

950
00:55:53,216 --> 00:55:56,853
Jin-ah / I’m glad the weather is nice today

951
00:55:57,854 --> 00:56:00,046
Han-kyul / Isn’t the sun too strong?

952
00:56:00,056 --> 00:56:02,592
Jin-ah / No, it’s fine

953
00:56:04,060 --> 00:56:05,551
Jin-ah / I really wanted to go out

954
00:56:05,561 --> 00:56:07,887
Jin-ah / I didn’t go out yesterday

955
00:56:07,897 --> 00:56:09,756
Jin-ah / I stayed in during the pottery too

956
00:56:09,766 --> 00:56:12,625
Han-kyul / You stayed inside all that time?

957
00:56:12,635 --> 00:56:15,972
Han-kyul / So it’s your first time out in two days?

958
00:56:16,172 --> 00:56:17,940
Jin-ah / Fresh air...

959
00:56:58,113 --> 00:57:01,340
Jin-ah / The place we went for our date

960
00:57:01,350 --> 00:57:03,475
Jin-ah / Was a vinyl cafe

961
00:57:03,485 --> 00:57:07,913
Jin-ah / I looked at Han-kyul next to me and saw this wild look in her eyes

962
00:57:07,923 --> 00:57:12,918
Jin-ah / Like she had so much to say and was super interested

963
00:57:12,928 --> 00:57:14,620
Jin-ah / It was nice to see

964
00:57:14,630 --> 00:57:16,955
Jin-ah / I thought, “This is a good date”

965
00:57:16,965 --> 00:57:20,392
Han-kyul / Collecting vinyl is my hobby at home

966
00:57:20,402 --> 00:57:23,428
Han-kyul / Music is kind of my specialty

967
00:57:23,438 --> 00:57:26,265
Han-kyul / So I felt like I wanted to show that off a little

968
00:57:26,275 --> 00:57:28,400
Han-kyul / That’s how I felt

969
00:57:28,410 --> 00:57:31,436
Han-kyul / So I explained a bit about the player too

970
00:57:31,446 --> 00:57:32,504
Han-kyul / I thought that would be nice

971
00:57:32,514 --> 00:57:35,674
Han-kyul / And that made my eyes light up a little

972
00:57:35,684 --> 00:57:40,879
Jin-ah / I actually have a clear reason why I wanted to say something

973
00:57:40,889 --> 00:57:42,114
Han-kyul / Oh? Now I’m curious

974
00:57:42,124 --> 00:57:43,282
Jin-ah / Should we sit down?

975
00:57:43,292 --> 00:57:44,316
Jin-ah / Can I sit here?

976
00:57:44,326 --> 00:57:46,695
Han-kyul / Around here?

977
00:57:52,768 --> 00:57:55,561
Jin-ah / How do you listen to this?

978
00:57:55,571 --> 00:57:58,797
Han-kyul / Just plug in the headset

979
00:57:58,807 --> 00:58:02,668
Han-kyul / Normally you just listen through the headphones

980
00:58:02,678 --> 00:58:05,871
Han-kyul / The side with the cable is usually the left

981
00:58:05,881 --> 00:58:07,406
Han-kyul / The side with the cable

982
00:58:07,416 --> 00:58:12,444
Han-kyul / For wired headphones, anyway

983
00:58:12,454 --> 00:58:13,645
Jin-ah / It’s making weird sounds

984
00:58:13,655 --> 00:58:15,714
Han-kyul / Yeah, so this player

985
00:58:15,724 --> 00:58:18,851
Han-kyul / It makes really tiny scratching noises

986
00:58:18,861 --> 00:58:20,619
Han-kyul / The headphones just amplify that

987
00:58:20,629 --> 00:58:21,753
Han-kyul / The headphones...

988
00:58:21,763 --> 00:58:24,723
Han-kyul / Amplify those tiny sounds like this

989
00:58:24,733 --> 00:58:27,726
Han-kyul / So even if it’s not plugged in

990
00:58:27,736 --> 00:58:29,394
Han-kyul / If you put your ear to the needle

991
00:58:29,404 --> 00:58:32,197
Han-kyul / You can still hear the song

992
00:58:32,207 --> 00:58:35,500
Jin-ah / I’m glad I came here, you’re so cool

993
00:58:35,510 --> 00:58:38,470
Han-kyul / I have three players at home

994
00:58:38,480 --> 00:58:40,539
Han-kyul / Some for interior decor, some for actual use

995
00:58:40,549 --> 00:58:42,341
Han-kyul / I just started collecting them

996
00:58:42,351 --> 00:58:45,277
Jin-ah / Hearing that makes me want to start too

997
00:58:45,287 --> 00:58:48,280
Jin-ah / Can I go first and play something? Because

998
00:58:48,290 --> 00:58:50,549
Jin-ah / I really like a song called “Cigarettes After Sex”

999
00:58:50,559 --> 00:58:51,783
Jin-ah / There’s a song I love...

1000
00:58:51,793 --> 00:58:53,018
Han-kyul / What is it?

1001
00:58:53,028 --> 00:58:57,022
Jin-ah / Just... some really popular ones?

1002
00:58:57,032 --> 00:59:00,525
Jin-ah / Stuff like that, but they’re not here

1003
00:59:00,535 --> 00:59:04,229
Han-kyul / My favorite album has the song “Cry” in it

1004
00:59:04,239 --> 00:59:08,600
Han-kyul / I really love the lyrics of that song

1005
00:59:08,610 --> 00:59:12,905
Han-kyul / It says, “If you love me, I’ll probably make you cry”

1006
00:59:12,915 --> 00:59:16,008
Han-kyul / But it feels like the one saying that

1007
00:59:16,018 --> 00:59:18,911
Han-kyul / Is actually the one crying more on the inside

1008
00:59:18,921 --> 00:59:22,724
Jin-ah / I really got that feeling too

1009
00:59:25,861 --> 00:59:28,887
Han-kyul / “Because I’m someone who can’t love deeply or for long

1010
00:59:28,897 --> 00:59:32,234
Han-kyul / If we love, you’re going to cry”

1011
00:59:33,201 --> 00:59:35,994
Han-kyul / That’s what it says, but while listening

1012
00:59:36,004 --> 00:59:37,963
Han-kyul / I felt like the person saying that

1013
00:59:37,973 --> 00:59:41,166
Han-kyul / Is actually crying even more inside

1014
00:59:41,176 --> 00:59:43,669
Han-kyul / Like they were pretending or covering it up

1015
00:59:43,679 --> 00:59:45,180
Han-kyul / That’s what I thought

1016
00:59:46,014 --> 00:59:49,441
Jin-ah / I’m so glad you know how to do this

1017
00:59:49,451 --> 00:59:53,121
Jin-ah / I probably would’ve asked the staff for help

1018
00:59:54,723 --> 00:59:58,760
Jin-ah / Oh I can hear it

1019
01:00:22,284 --> 01:00:25,744
Han-kyul / The song is called “Cry” and the lyrics are

1020
01:00:25,754 --> 01:00:28,947
Han-kyul / “There’s something I need to tell you first”

1021
01:00:28,957 --> 01:00:32,351
Han-kyul / “If we fall in love, you’re bound to cry”

1022
01:00:32,361 --> 01:00:35,520
Han-kyul / I once cried just listening to that alone

1023
01:00:35,530 --> 01:00:38,623
Han-kyul / So I kind of wanted to share

1024
01:00:38,633 --> 01:00:42,270
Han-kyul / “This is what resonates with me as a person”

1025
01:00:47,242 --> 01:00:50,379
Jin-ah / I almost cried... I was kind of...

1026
01:00:50,679 --> 01:00:53,305
Han-kyul / Did it get through to you?

1027
01:00:53,315 --> 01:00:55,674
Jin-ah / Yeah, well...

1028
01:00:55,684 --> 01:01:00,445
Jin-ah / First of all, it’s the lyrics and the voice

1029
01:01:00,455 --> 01:01:03,882
Han-kyul / Right? The voice really has... conviction

1030
01:01:03,892 --> 01:01:06,785
Jin-ah / That part when they sing “Cry”...

1031
01:01:06,795 --> 01:01:09,554
Jin-ah / It felt... it felt like you

1032
01:01:09,564 --> 01:01:12,791
Han-kyul / I used to play it late at night and cry alone

1033
01:01:12,801 --> 01:01:15,971
Jin-ah / Seriously, that’s such a “Han-kyul pick”

1034
01:01:23,879 --> 01:01:26,815
Jin-ah / This part

1035
01:01:31,553 --> 01:01:36,181
Han-kyul / Even in music preferences like this

1036
01:01:36,191 --> 01:01:39,818
Han-kyul / I felt like we had a connection. Like this was fate

1037
01:01:39,828 --> 01:01:41,353
Han-kyul / That’s what I thought

1038
01:01:41,363 --> 01:01:43,789
Jin-ah / With Han-kyul’s sparkling eyes

1039
01:01:43,799 --> 01:01:46,591
Jin-ah / We went on a date while sharing music

1040
01:01:46,601 --> 01:01:50,796
Jin-ah / I’m also someone who really takes lyrics to heart

1041
01:01:50,806 --> 01:01:52,664
Jin-ah / I pick songs based on that

1042
01:01:52,674 --> 01:01:55,400
Jin-ah / It went beyond “we get along well when we talk”

1043
01:01:55,410 --> 01:02:01,239
Jin-ah / Han-kyul’s eyes at that moment were just so cool

1044
01:02:01,249 --> 01:02:04,609
Jin-ah / Yeah, I liked that part too

1045
01:02:04,619 --> 01:02:06,912
Han-kyul / We both cried in the past

1046
01:02:06,922 --> 01:02:08,747
Han-kyul / And we both picked songs with “Cry”

1047
01:02:08,757 --> 01:02:12,828
Han-kyul / That felt kind of symbolic

1048
01:02:13,728 --> 01:02:17,189
Han-kyul / But it’s okay, crying is a meaningful experience

1049
01:02:17,199 --> 01:02:20,592
Jin-ah / Crying really helped me let things out, and also

1050
01:02:20,602 --> 01:02:23,161
Jin-ah / You all joke about my “cool act”

1051
01:02:23,171 --> 01:02:25,831
Jin-ah / But my coolness is being cheerful

1052
01:02:25,841 --> 01:02:27,766
Han-kyul / Cheerfulness is your version of cool?

1053
01:02:27,776 --> 01:02:30,602
Jin-ah / I never want to show weakness in front of others

1054
01:02:30,612 --> 01:02:33,338
Han-kyul / But do you think you only gain positives

1055
01:02:33,348 --> 01:02:36,942
Han-kyul / By always doing that?

1056
01:02:36,952 --> 01:02:39,411
Jin-ah / No! I don’t usually act like that outside

1057
01:02:39,421 --> 01:02:41,446
Jin-ah / But I think I did that more here

1058
01:02:41,456 --> 01:02:45,917
Han-kyul / But when you keep suppressing things like that

1059
01:02:45,927 --> 01:02:47,352
Han-kyul / It eventually just bursts out

1060
01:02:47,362 --> 01:02:51,356
Jin-ah / Honestly, it’s not about liking or disliking people

1061
01:02:51,366 --> 01:02:53,735
Jin-ah / Some people just don’t click with you, you know?

1062
01:02:55,437 --> 01:03:01,433
Jin-ah / I don’t really engage with people I don’t click with

1063
01:03:01,443 --> 01:03:03,268
Jin-ah / There’s no need to

1064
01:03:03,278 --> 01:03:06,438
Han-kyul / I’ve realized that too in life

1065
01:03:06,448 --> 01:03:08,740
Han-kyul / People call it “being on the same wavelength”

1066
01:03:08,750 --> 01:03:11,843
Han-kyul / But you don’t find that very often

1067
01:03:11,853 --> 01:03:14,579
Han-kyul / So when you do meet someone like that

1068
01:03:14,589 --> 01:03:17,149
Han-kyul / You shouldn't let them go so easily

1069
01:03:17,159 --> 01:03:21,586
Han-kyul / I used to have this image of older women

1070
01:03:21,596 --> 01:03:22,587
Han-kyul / A certain idea, like

1071
01:03:22,597 --> 01:03:25,023
Han-kyul / Someone really overwhelmingly cool

1072
01:03:25,033 --> 01:03:26,591
Jin-ah / Hee-young? Oh yeah yeah yeah

1073
01:03:26,601 --> 01:03:28,927
Han-kyul / I kind of thought

1074
01:03:28,937 --> 01:03:33,231
Han-kyul / If I could be with someone like that, that would be great

1075
01:03:33,241 --> 01:03:35,367
Han-kyul / I wanted to be loved like that

1076
01:03:35,377 --> 01:03:40,105
Han-kyul / I thought that was the kind of person I was

1077
01:03:40,115 --> 01:03:43,842
Han-kyul / So I kept hinting at it indirectly

1078
01:03:43,852 --> 01:03:48,446
Han-kyul / Like saying I wanted to do a fan meeting or something

1079
01:03:48,456 --> 01:03:51,449
Han-kyul / But then suddenly I started thinking

1080
01:03:51,459 --> 01:03:54,986
Han-kyul / You were always alone, hurting and crying

1081
01:03:54,996 --> 01:03:57,222
Han-kyul / Your eyes were always teary

1082
01:03:57,232 --> 01:03:58,690
Han-kyul / Watching that

1083
01:03:58,700 --> 01:04:00,325
Han-kyul / I couldn’t take it anymore

1084
01:04:00,335 --> 01:04:03,328
Han-kyul / I couldn’t just keep watching you like that

1085
01:04:03,338 --> 01:04:07,999
Han-kyul / Because I felt like, “I wouldn’t make her feel that way”

1086
01:04:08,009 --> 01:04:09,067
Han-kyul / If it were me?

1087
01:04:09,077 --> 01:04:12,037
Han-kyul / So in a way

1088
01:04:12,047 --> 01:04:15,473
Han-kyul / Age or who leads the relationship

1089
01:04:15,483 --> 01:04:17,509
Han-kyul / Those things aren’t everything

1090
01:04:17,519 --> 01:04:19,678
Han-kyul / That’s what I realized

1091
01:04:19,688 --> 01:04:24,349
Han-kyul / Then I wanted to make you happy

1092
01:04:24,359 --> 01:04:27,586
Han-kyul / But honestly, I can’t say things like that so easily

1093
01:04:27,596 --> 01:04:30,589
Han-kyul / Because I’m not the type who can offer instant security

1094
01:04:30,599 --> 01:04:32,190
Han-kyul / I’m not that kind of person

1095
01:04:32,200 --> 01:04:37,062
Han-kyul / Even so, if you’re crying and hurting and sad like that

1096
01:04:37,072 --> 01:04:39,898
Han-kyul / I didn’t want to leave you like that

1097
01:04:39,908 --> 01:04:42,367
Han-kyul / I didn’t want that to continue

1098
01:04:42,377 --> 01:04:45,470
Han-kyul / But then I revealed my age

1099
01:04:45,480 --> 01:04:48,139
Han-kyul / And I honestly thought that once I did

1100
01:04:48,149 --> 01:04:50,609
Han-kyul / No one would be interested in me

1101
01:04:50,619 --> 01:04:52,110
Han-kyul / That they wouldn’t give me a chance

1102
01:04:52,120 --> 01:04:53,478
Han-kyul / So I just gave up

1103
01:04:53,488 --> 01:04:56,114
Han-kyul / But that night, you called me

1104
01:04:56,124 --> 01:04:59,284
Han-kyul / And by doing that, you gave me hope

1105
01:04:59,294 --> 01:05:03,355
Han-kyul / So I wanted to take that chance

1106
01:05:03,365 --> 01:05:05,890
Han-kyul / I wanted to give it a shot

1107
01:05:05,900 --> 01:05:10,939
Han-kyul / Willingly and wholeheartedly

1108
01:05:12,374 --> 01:05:15,667
Jin-ah / I was sitting next to Han-kyul

1109
01:05:15,677 --> 01:05:20,105
Jin-ah / And I thought, “She’s so beautiful”

1110
01:05:20,115 --> 01:05:24,075
Jin-ah / I’ve never loved someone with long hair before

1111
01:05:24,085 --> 01:05:26,945
Jin-ah / She’s both cool and pretty

1112
01:05:26,955 --> 01:05:28,647
Jin-ah / She has a kind of beauty that’s different from mine

1113
01:05:28,657 --> 01:05:32,150
Jin-ah / Honestly, it felt like when I had my very first girlfriend

1114
01:05:32,160 --> 01:05:36,488
Jin-ah / It was like a whole new expansion in loving women

1115
01:05:36,498 --> 01:05:38,223
Jin-ah / For me personally

1116
01:05:38,233 --> 01:05:41,026
Jin-ah / It was such a wondrous moment

1117
01:05:41,036 --> 01:05:43,361
Han-kyul / I just wanted to say, “I hope you’re happy”

1118
01:05:43,371 --> 01:05:46,131
Han-kyul / But I felt like if I said only that

1119
01:05:46,141 --> 01:05:49,901
Han-kyul / It might not sound convincing enough

1120
01:05:49,911 --> 01:05:52,237
Han-kyul / So I kind of tried to hint

1121
01:05:52,247 --> 01:05:53,505
Han-kyul / That maybe she could see me

1122
01:05:53,515 --> 01:05:57,252
Han-kyul / As someone she could date

1123
01:06:08,563 --> 01:06:10,689
Jin-ah / I was wondering earlier

1124
01:06:10,699 --> 01:06:13,658
Jin-ah / When was the last time you came to Jeju?

1125
01:06:13,668 --> 01:06:16,194
Han-kyul / July 2022

1126
01:06:16,204 --> 01:06:16,995
Jin-ah / Why? Just for fun?

1127
01:06:17,005 --> 01:06:18,963
Han-kyul / Yeah, just a trip...

1128
01:06:18,973 --> 01:06:26,438
Jin-ah / I was on this road last spring too, I think

1129
01:06:26,448 --> 01:06:28,606
Jin-ah / I love this area, Aewol

1130
01:06:28,616 --> 01:06:31,609
Han-kyul / This really feels like Jeju, you know?

1131
01:06:31,619 --> 01:06:33,688
Jin-ah / I’m so happy right now

1132
01:06:38,960 --> 01:06:41,720
Jin-ah / I love filming planes

1133
01:06:41,730 --> 01:06:43,431
Jin-ah / No reason

1134
01:06:55,610 --> 01:06:58,403
Jin-ah / Maybe it’s because I love Jeju trips so much

1135
01:06:58,413 --> 01:07:00,205
Jin-ah / I just wanted to kidnap Han-kyul

1136
01:07:00,215 --> 01:07:02,273
Jin-ah / And go on a Jeju trip with just the two of us

1137
01:07:02,283 --> 01:07:03,742
Jin-ah / That’s what I thought

1138
01:07:03,752 --> 01:07:06,745
Jin-ah / And right now, I’m just so happy with her

1139
01:07:06,755 --> 01:07:08,146
Jin-ah / When we go back to the house

1140
01:07:08,156 --> 01:07:09,514
Jin-ah / There’s someone who thinks

1141
01:07:09,524 --> 01:07:11,960
Jin-ah / I stole Han-kyul away

1142
01:07:12,761 --> 01:07:17,399
Jin-ah / So going back doesn’t feel so great

1143
01:07:18,166 --> 01:07:19,357
Jin-ah / Should we go?

1144
01:07:19,367 --> 01:07:23,338
Jin-ah / I’m hungry

1145
01:07:25,473 --> 01:07:26,998
Han-kyul / I think only now

1146
01:07:27,008 --> 01:07:30,378
Han-kyul / I’m finally starting to get used to Jeju
